description: Just days after Angela Merkel loosens restrictions, the estimated virus reproduction rate rises.
title: Coronavirus: Germany infection rate rises as lockdown eases
title_page: Coronavirus: Germany infection rate rises as lockdown eases - BBC News
maintext: At the same time though the daily death toll in Germany is the lowest it's been in more than a month. Fewer than 40 people here died of Covid-19 in the 24 hours until Sunday. In other large European countries this level has at times risen to almost 1,000.
